data.description: Looking for SPACE, this home has it! Almost 3000 sq ft w/ every room being SPACIOUS! Roof only a couple years old. Walk in & be taken back by the beauty of the wide dark hardwood floors! Elegantly designed staircase makes a great focal point when you walk in spacious foyer. Living room has so much beauty, from the bold fireplace, exposed beams, exquisite trim work & plantation blinds. Additional living space in den & heated/cooled sunroom. Kitchen is generously sized, features butcher block style counters w/ stone backsplash, oversized center island w/ cooktop & lots of storage, also nice size pantry. Gorgeous large window that lets in lots of natural light. Large laundry/mud room off kitchen. Upstairs you will find 3 LARGE bedrooms, including master w/ hardwoods. Upstairs landing is super spacious w/ room for a sitting area or office. Outside you will find a MASSIVE deck, perfect for entertaining & creek w/ waterfall literally on the backside of property. Home has great curb appeal.
